files.description: The sole EHI export documentation for MedPointe. A 2-page PDF describing how to export clinical documents using a proprietary 'C62' file format. Covers single document, chart, and batch export workflows via the MedPointe UI. Does not include a data dictionary, schema, format specification, or description of what data is exported. Author: Tim Schmidt. Created: 2023-11-16.
files.curl_command: curl -sL 'https://downloads.hstcentral.com/helpdocs/Exporting%20Documents/Providers%20-%20Exporting%20Computer%20Readable%20Documents.pdf' -H 'User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0' -o 'Providers - Exporting Computer Readable Documents.pdf'
